strings:
<voice_0x01000C0C><se_def>Angelo: That sinister presence again...
No, not sinister... It's worse than that...
<voice_0x01000C0D><se_def>Angelo: It's pure evil... As if all the demons of hell had gathered to feast upon...

<voice_0x01000C10><se_def>Angelo: Marcello! Are you in there!?
Damn! What's going on!?
<voice_0x01000C11><se_def>Angelo: It's no good! It won't budge!
<voice_0x01000C12><se_def>Angelo: You lot...! Did you follow me here?

<voice_0x01000C13><se_def>Angelo: Doesn't matter! I need your help!
Just one last time, all right!?

<voice_0x01000C14><se_def>Angelo: We're going to have to do this by brute force.
There might just be enough of us!

<voice_0x01000C15><se_def>Angelo: The door's locked from the inside.
We've got to break it down!
Come on, everyone together!
